    • Method Detail

      • testConsoleQuit

        public void testConsoleQuit()
        Tests the quit command of the interactive console. Asserts that:
        • the program can be terminated by running the command quit
        • (Implicatory) the program is not terminated by System.exit(x) with x>0
        • the program does not output anything when being terminated through quit
